Description: Usage
        -----
        
        .. code:: python
        
            from django.http import HttpResponse
            from djbrut import Attempt
        
            def some_view(request):
                attempt = Attempt(request)
                # check
                if not attempt.check():
                    # error
                    return HttpResponse(attempt.error)
                # success
                ...
        
